  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Smart Video Doorbell",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti UVC-G4-DoorBell G4 Doorbell is an advanced, WiFi-connected smart doorbell equipped with a high-definition night vision camera and a built-in porch light. It boasts a 2MP video resolution and provides up to 6 meters of infrared night vision, enabling clear footage even in complete darkness."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Enhanced Security and Integration",
      "text": "The device integrates artificial intelligence for event detection, enhancing security and operational efficiency. It connects wirelessly through UniFi WiFi Auto-Link, facilitating seamless integration into existing networks. Additionally, the G4 Doorbell features two-way audio communication, allowing for direct interaction with visitors. Its construction is IPX4 weather-resistant, making it suitable for outdoor installation in covered areas. This product exemplifies modern security technology, combining convenience with robust surveillance capabilities. Integration with UniFi Protect provides an easy-to-use interface."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Features",
      "text": "- 1600x1200 (2MP) HD stream with night vision\n- Integrated entrance lighting\n- Real-time two-way audio with echo cancellation\n- Built-in display\n- Dual-band 802.11ac Wi-Fi\n- PIR motion detection sensor\n- Weather-resistant\n- UniFi Protect integration"
    },
    {
      "heading": "Note",
      "text": "UniFI Protect is required to run this product with full functionality, Ubiquiti recommend using it with UniFi Dream Machine PRO, UniFi Protect Network Video Recorder or Cloud Key Gen2 Plus."
    }
  ],
